  Migrating away from deprecated postgres virtuals

  26 Jan 2010; Patrick Lauer <patrick@gentoo.org> motion-3.2.11.1.ebuild:
  Fixing postgres dep for #300908

  19 Jan 2010; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
